<div class="content_wrapper">
<div id="form_wrapper">
	<h1> Add New User </h1>
	<div id="add_patient medications">
		<form action="/add_prescription" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="new_user">
			<p>Doctor  
			<input type="text" name="prescribed_by" id="new_prescription[prescribed_by]"> 
			says I need to take  
			<select type="text" name="number" id="new_prescription[number]">
				<option value="1">1</option>
				<option value="2">2</option>
				<option value="3">3</option>
				<option value="4">4</option>
				<option value="5">5</option>
				<option value="6">6</option>
			</select>  
			doses of  
			<input type="text" name="medication" id="new_prescription[medication]"> 
			every 
			<input type="text" name="hours" id="new_prescription[hours]">
			hours, for my 
			<input type="text" name="condition" id="new_prescription[condition]">.</p>
			
			<p>The basic information reguarding my medication is  
			<input type="text" name="basic_info" id="new_prescription[basic_info]">  
			and the side effects are
			<input type="text" name="side_effects" id="new_prescription[side_effects]" >.</p>
			
			<p>All warnings and issues I should be aware of reguarding my medication are 
			<input type="text" name="warnings" id="new_prescription[warnings]">.</p>
			
			<p>My user name is
			<input type="text" name="username" id="new_prescription[username]" value="<%= @user %>"></p>
			
			<input type="submit">
		</form>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
